==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Empressement
<hw>Em`presse`ment"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., fr
<ets>s'empresser</ets> to hasten.]</ety> <def>Demonstrative warmth or
cordiality of manner; display of enthusiasm.</def></p>

<p><q>He grasped my hand with a nervous <qex>empressement</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Poe.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Emprint</ent>⟦br⟧
